name: Get Back To Camp
description:
You've lost your coat, get up off your knees and get back to camp!
if the cold doesn't get to you first...

Press Space to start.

if the intro glitches, just press green flag again.

Made by TripleA games,
Game dev students from Algonquin college,

- The Lonely Traveler ~ Coding & concept

- Fol.lys - Art/Assets
